data.description: WELCOME INVESTOR'S!  CASH OFFER'S ONLY!  GREAT INVESTMENT PROPERTY! TWO FAMILY DETACHED LOCATED IN CLASON POINT/SOUNDVIEW.  Welcome to 306 Harding Park the first floor boasts 2 bedrooms, kitchen, living room and a full bathroom. Second floor consists of a three bedroom, master suite bedroom has its own full bathroom, 2 full bathroom and a kitchen. The third unit has 2 bedrooms, full bathroom, living room and kitchen.  Sold "as is" with violations!  Outside has a driveway, 2 sheds++ and a huge patio overlooking the East River.  Conveniently located close to public transportation and Soundview Ferry that takes you into Manhattan.
